Malden, MA: Polity Press.</li>

<li>Hare, J., 2006, <em>God and Morality A Philosophical History</em>,
Oxford: Blackwell.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1996, <em>The Moral Gap</em>, Oxford:
