Clarendon Press.</li>

<li>Hare, R. M., 1981, <em>Moral Thinking</em>, Oxford: Clarendon
Press.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1992, &ldquo;The Simple Believer,&rdquo;
<em>Essays on Religion and Education</em>, Oxford: Clarendon
Press.</li>

<li>Herdt, Jennifer A., 1997, <em>Religion and Faction in Hume&rsquo;s
Moral Philosophy</em>. Cambridge: Cambridge University Press.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2022, <em>Assuming Responsibility: Ecstatic
Eudaimonism and the Call to Live Well</em>, Oxford: Oxford University
Press.</li>

<li>Hourani, George, 1971, <em>Islamic Rationalism</em>: <em>The
