Oxford; Oxford University Press.</li>

<li>MacIntyre, Alasdair, 1988, <em>Whose Justice, Which
Rationality</em>, London: Duckworth.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2016. <em>Ethics in the Conflicts of
Modernity</em>. Cambridge: Cambridge University Press.</li>

<li>Mikalson, J., 1991, <em>Honor Thy Gods</em>, Chapel Hill: The
University of North Carolina Press.</li>

<li>Porter, J., 1999, <em>Natural and Divine Law</em>, Grand Rapids,
MI: Eerdmans.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2005, <em>Nature as Reason</em>, Grand
Rapids, MI: Eerdmans.</li>

<li>Quinn, P., 1978, <em>Divine Commands and Moral Requirements</em>,
Oxford: Oxford University Press.</li>

