University Press.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1971, <em>A Theory of Justice</em>,
Cambridge, MA: Harvard University Press.</li>

<li>Rudolph, Ulrich, 2014, <em>Al-Maturidi and Sunni Theology in
Samarkand</em>, Leiden: Brill.</li>

<li>Schneewind, J., 1998, <em>The Invention of Autonomy</em>,
Cambridge: Cambridge University Press.</li>

